ies) episodes#Webby Reacts|Webby Reacts]]'''|| 7 || May 8, 2018 || May 26, 2018\n|- \n| style=\"background: #FFA500;\"| \n|'''[[List of DuckTales (2017 TV series) episodes#The World's Longest Deathtrap!|The World's Longest Deathtrap!]]''' || 5 || May 27, 2018 || June 24, 2018 \n|-\n| style=\"background: #6A4794\"|\n| '''[[List of DuckTales (2017 TV series) episodes#Fly|Fly]]'''|| 1 || colspan=\"2\"| June 23, 2018\n|- \n| style=\"background: #00FFFF\"| \n| '''[[List of DuckTales (2017 TV series) episodes#Dewey Dew-Night!|Dewey Dew-Night!]]'''|| 4 || July 8, 2018 || July 29, 2018\n|- \n| style=\"background: #000000\"|\n| '''[[List of DuckTales (2017 TV series) episodes#Disney Theme Song Takeover|Disney Theme Song Takeover]]'''|| 2 || June 27, 2019 || July 19, 2019\n|-\n| style=\"background: #A61270\"|\n| '''[[List of DuckTales (2017 TV series) episodes#Top 4 Favorites|Top 4 Favorites]]'''|| 5 || July 23, 2019 || August 25, 2019\n|}\n</onlyinclude>\n\n====Welcome to Duckburg!====\nReleased through the Disney XD YouTube channel ahead of the show's premiere, these shorts spotlight several characters.\n{{Episode table |background=A52A2A |overall=5 |title=37 |director=17 |writer=18 |airdate=23 |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 1\n| Title           = Donald's Birthday\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|6|9}}\n| ShortSummary    = Uncle Scrooge, Huey, Dewey, Louie and Webby help Donald celebrate his birthday!\n| LineColor       = A52A2A\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 2\n| Title           = Meet Scrooge!\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|6|9}}\n| ShortSummary    = Scrooge and Louie tussle with a mysterious clock.\n| LineColor       = A52A2A\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 3\n| Title           = Meet Huey!\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|6|9}}\n| ShortSummary    = Huey goes camping with the help of h