ble!\n| LineColor       = FFC0CB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 2\n| Title           = 30 Things With Webby\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|2}}\n| ShortSummary    = Meet Webby! She likes churros, secret passageways and...sword horses? She\u2019s also the #1 fan girl of the McDuck family! \n| LineColor       = FFC0CB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 3\n| Title           = 30 Things With Dewey\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|3}}\n| ShortSummary    = Meet Dewey! He likes hair zooshing, moonwalking into a room for dramatic effect, and looking into the face of danger!\n| LineColor       = FFC0CB\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 4\n| Title           = 30 Things With Louie\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|4}}\n| ShortSummary    = Meet Louie! He likes watching TV, rocking a hoodie, and getting away with everything! He charms his way into \u2013 and out of \u2013 danger!\n| LineColor       = FFC0CB\n}}\n}}\n\n====Webby Reacts====\nThese shorts are \"[[reaction video]]s\" featuring Webby watching another Disney Channel show.\n{{Episode table |background=006600 |overall=5 |title=37 |director=17 |writer=18 |airdate=23 |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 1\n| Title           = Webby Reacts To: ''[[Andi Mack]]''\" - \"Bex's Secret\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|8}}\n| ShortSummary    = Webby Vanderquack discovers her new best rhyme friend Andi Mack but isn't ready for the family secret revealed! Or is she?\n| LineColor       = 006600\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 2\n| Title           = Webby Reacts To: ''[[Andi Mack]]''\" - \"Ummm\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|10}}\n| ShortSummary    = Ready for another episode of Andi Mack, Webby fires up her TV phone for some\u2026awkward silence?  Is \u201cummm\u201d even an answer?\n| LineColor       = 006600\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 3\n| Title           = Webby Reacts To: ''[[Zombies (2018 film)|ZOMBIES]]''\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|12}}\n| ShortSummary    = Darkness\u2026music\u2026a blinking red light. With her crossbow by her side, Webby knows this means danger is ahead for Zed and Addison!\n| LineColor       = 006600\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 4\n| Title           = Webby Reacts To: ''[[Stuck in the Middle (TV series)|Stuck in the Middle]]''\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|16}}\n| ShortSummary    = When Webby can't get a hold of #allthefeels over Rachel's goodbye, she gets a hold of Huey, Dewey and Louie instead!\n| LineColor       = 006600\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 5\n| Title           = Webby Reacts To: ''[[Raven's Home]]''\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|18}}\n| ShortSummary    = Webby tries to tell Nia ([[Navia Robinson]]) that shapeshifters and sirens are no match against the power of pizza!\n| LineColor       = 006600\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 6\n| Title           = Webby Reacts To: ''[[Descendants 2]]''\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|24}}\n| ShortSummary    = Webby can't understand why VK Uma ([[China Anne McClain]]) can remember all those dance moves, but not her own name!\n| LineColor       = 006600\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 7\n| Title           = Webby Reacts To: ''[[Descendants 3]]''\n| DirectedBy      = \n| WrittenBy       = \n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|5|26}}\n| ShortSummary    = Webby taps into her inner Descendants fangirl and discovers Mal ([[Dove Cameron]]) has her own family mystery to uncover!\n| LineColor       = 006600\n}}\n}}\n\n====The World's Longest Deathtrap!====\